data.description: Absolutely lovely 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home with a bonus room in the Ocean Springs School District on a fantastic cul du sac!  Large open kitchen/living/dining area. Beautiful gas fireplace.  Large walk-in closet in the spacious primary bedroom. Primary ensuite has dual vanity sinks, jetted tub and separate shower.  Upstairs boasts 3 bedrooms, a bonus room ad a full bathroom.  This home is NOT in a flood zone and qualifies for USDA financing!
